        "briefDescription": "Under the “Distribution of Soil Health Card” scheme, Soil health cards will be distributed to all the farmers who have offered the soil sample for testing by paying a prescribed fee of ₹5/- each for Macro and Micronutrient testing.\n\n",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Under the “Distribution of Soil Health Card” scheme, by the Agriculture-Farmers Welfare Department, Tamil Nadu, Soil health cards will be distributed to all the farmers who have offered the soil sample for testing by paying a prescribed fee of ₹5/- each for Macro and Micronutrient testing.\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- Soil Health Cards to farmers.\n\n<br>\n\n",
